        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2142518353" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1395070593275054605">One of my favorite accounts of man and the natural world, THE GOLDEN SPRUCE is such an amazing book. Vaillant does a superb job weaving the history of the logging industry into this tale of Native Americans and one white man who seemed to push himself over the edge. If you like books such as INTO THE WILD, don&apos;t miss this one. Just and extraordinary read.</span>
  <span id="freeText1395070593275054605" style="display:none">One of my favorite accounts of man and the natural world, THE GOLDEN SPRUCE is such an amazing book. Vaillant does a superb job weaving the history of the logging industry into this tale of Native Americans and one white man who seemed to push himself over the edge. If you like books such as INTO THE WILD, don't miss this one. Just and extraordinary read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1395070593275054605" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

